repository.name: zc_plugin_company_holiday_calendar
repository.description: This is calendar plugin developed with python, django, html, css and reactJs. It is part of the microservice zuri chat application and follows the monolithic software architecture. It writes, fetches and deletes its data from the zuri core system.
